{
  "id": "adv_event_2108_01_01",
  "title": "盗み聞き？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、おっはよーっ！\n今日もいい天気！　爽やかな朝だよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning everyone!\nIt’s fine weather again today! A fresh morning!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 6.566666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "……おはよ、芽衣",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Morning Mei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.766666666666667,
      "endTime": 10.398095194498698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます、昨夜はライブだったのに\nどうしてこんなに早起きなんですか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning. Why are you up so early‚ even after\nlast night’s live?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.6,
      "endTime": 17.566666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "まったくですわ、オフの日くらいゆっくり\n眠らせてほしいので――ふわっ……、くー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s too much. On a day off‚\nat least let me sleep… Zzz… zzz…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.766666666666666,
      "endTime": 29.681927744547526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "凄い、すずちゃん、立ったまま眠ってる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow. Suzu-chan is sleeping standing up…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.866666666666667,
      "endTime": 35.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、元気なのが芽衣の取柄だからねー！\nそれより大事なお話があるの、みんな座って座って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha. Because being lively is what I do best!\nBut I have something more important to talk about. Sit down‚ all of you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.46666666666667,
      "endTime": 45.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "大事な話？　何？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Something important? What is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.4,
      "endTime": 48.30909295082092,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんがさとみちゃんと\n立ち話してたのー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san was chatting\nwith Satomi-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.5,
      "endTime": 52.39999996821086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "それでね、物陰に隠れて\nたまたま聞いてたんだけど～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I was standing behind something‚\nand I happened to overhear…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.6,
      "endTime": 57.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "物陰に隠れてって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Standing behind something”…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.56666666666667,
      "endTime": 59.66666661898295,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣ちゃん、それ盗み聞きなんじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei-chan‚ that’s called eavesdropping…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.86666666666667,
      "endTime": 65.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、二人が真面目にしゃべってる\n横顔をじーっと見てたら、お話終わっちゃってたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hee hee. I was watching the two\ntalk really seriously‚ and it was over before I knew it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.33333333333333,
      "endTime": 73.77536258697509,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "もう、芽衣ちゃんったら何を言ってるんですか\nそれで{user}さん達のお話って……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei-chan‚ what are you talking about?\nSo‚ what were {user}-san saying?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.96666666666667,
      "endTime": 80.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣達のこと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was about us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.06666666666666,
      "endTime": 83.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "私達……月のテンペストのことを？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Us… about Moon Tempest?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.23333333333333,
      "endTime": 86.43333342870076,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "なんでしょう。昨日のライブはうまくいきましたし\n何も問題はないはずですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saying what? Last night’s show went well.\nThere shouldn’t be any problem…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.63333333333334,
      "endTime": 93.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "むにゃむにゃ、やりましたわ……ついに、私が\nトップアイドルの頂点に……すかー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*mumble* I did it‚ at last!\nI’m the pinnacle of top idols…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.8,
      "endTime": 105.43625403051978,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "トップアイドルの頂点って、意味かぶってるよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Pinnacle of top idols”… pinnacle and top is the same thing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.63333333333334,
      "endTime": 109.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃんは、そろそろ起きましょうね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu-chan‚ you should wake up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.13333333333334,
      "endTime": 113.08984130223593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣、それよりどんな話だったのか教えて\n悪い話なら、早急にみんなで話し合わないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei‚ tell us what they were saying.\nIf it’s something bad‚ we all need to discuss it quickly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.3,
      "endTime": 120.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "違う違う！　悪い話なわけないじゃん！\n逆だよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No no! It wasn’t anything bad!\nQuite the opposite!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.36666666666666,
      "endTime": 125.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "月のテンペストに、IDOL beach Fesの\n出演依頼が来てるんだって！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Moon Tempest has been asked to\nperform at IDOL beach Fes!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.63333333333334,
      "endTime": 130.66891891891893,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "IDOL beach Fesって、福岡のビーチで\n毎年やってる大きなフェス……。それに私達が？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "IDOL beach Fes is the big festival they have\nevery year on the beach in Fukuoka. They want us?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.9,
      "endTime": 139.00000000000003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "そう！　しかも二番目に\n大きいステージのトリなんだって～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! As second headliner‚\nperforming the closing act on the big stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.16666666666666,
      "endTime": 143.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "トリを務めてきたアイドルは、凄い顔ぶれね\n凄い……ここに私達が？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The idols who performed the closing act there are all legends.\nWow… and we’ll be there?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.86666666666667,
      "endTime": 151.91695633754932,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "それにビーチだよ！　お仕事のついでに\nバカンスも楽しめちゃうかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And on the beach! We can have a\nvacation after work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.13333333333333,
      "endTime": 157.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "バカンス……わ、私は少しも興味ありませんけど\n大きな仕事なら……ねぇ、琴乃ちゃん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Vacation… I’m not even slightly interested in that‚\nbut if it’s a big job… Right‚ Kotono-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.9,
      "endTime": 165.93333333333337,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "うん、絶対やりたい\nこんなチャンス逃したくない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yup‚ I want to do it for sure.\nI don’t want to miss this opportunity.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.13333333333333,
      "endTime": 170.39999999999998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "だよね～{user}さんは最近忙しいから\nオフにした方がいいかなって悩んでたんだけど～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right? {user}-san was worrying that\nwe’ve been too busy lately and should take a break instead.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.6,
      "endTime": 178.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
